    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">5–14</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The strategic value of -OUS lies in vowel management. When your rack is vowel-heavy (O and U are often considered "dead" vowels), -OUS converts them into productive plays. It's also an S-dump — using one of your precious S tiles constructively rather than just pluralizing.</p>

