    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Vowel dump strategy:</span> When your rack has too many vowels (especially O and U), look for -OUS plays. JOYOUS uses J+Y+O+O+U+S — it deploys three vowels while scoring 16 points. Much better than exchanging tiles.</p>
